  <text>
	Nuggets don't have much of a crafting use, besides <style color="0xbbffaa">Iron Nuggets</style> being able to be smelted into <style color="0xbbffaa">Wrought Iron Nuggets</style> 
	and the odd nugget which can be turned into a <style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:materials/round" underlined="true">Round</style>, like this 
	nuggets mainly function as smaller material units for the purpose of (for example)
	<style color="0xafff00" hover-info="click link" link="gtceu:machines/arc_furnace" underlined="true">Arc Furnace</style> recycling.
  </text>
